{"tid":510351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［暗瘡撚］喊出黎 有冇人可以講我知會點？","createTime":"2017-12-26T11:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T07:37:34.000Z","uid":160050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7acc7aa4377895b24c5c557fc5f5ea6e4bc3eda5","tid":510351,"uid":160050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"話說今日同屋企人去睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我依加就食緊個minocycline(四環素）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我驚整唔見左啲藥 所以比左屋企人保管<br />\n以為實無死啦 點知問屋企人拎番個時 <br />\n啲藥已經唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲可以教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經問左好多地方 靜係醫生先有個隻藥<br />\n好驚停左藥就狂生暗瘡呀 救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e316d5a31554dfe583d1f3fbcd5c747fe0253ad4","tid":510351,"uid":158738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"咁咪再叫醫生開藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4928d86cad49a3e16093285398ba6554fe08c5a8","tid":510351,"uid":163458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"信我 快d食a 酸 唔好慳個d錢 其實負作用唔大 只係乾d  不過食完一個療程真係可以幾年唔會再生 推薦oratane<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/112928_3059dfb28dadc9467d674d379f752042.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F112928_3059dfb28dadc9467d674d379f752042.jpeg&h=300f1493&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9de2053991155a70b5872cc8c28497673bd828ed","tid":510351,"uid":160050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4928d86cad49a3e16093285398ba6554fe08c5a8","tid":510351,"uid":163458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:29:32.000